        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Coordination Of Medicare Payments and Workers' Compensation Act or the COMP Act</b></p> <p>This bill alters provisions relating to Medicare secondary payer rules with respect to workers' compensation settlement arrangements. Among other things, the bill provides that a Medicare set-aside fulfills secondary payer obligations if the set-aside is included in the arrangement and meets certain other criteria.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
